    "texts": [
     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"We believe the best way to keep children safe is to teach them road safety from a very early age. Educating children today creates responsible road users for the future.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "Here are some examples of how we tailor our road safety message to youngsters of all ages:",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"strong\"}",
     "Our \u003ca href=\"/info-for/schools-and-young-people/teaching-resources/children-s-traffic-club-london\"\u003eChildren's Traffic Club London\u003c/a\u003e uses interactive DVDs, activity books and fun activities to teach pre-school children simple but vital road safety skills.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"strong\"}",
     "With our \u003ca href=\"/info-for/schools-and-young-people/teaching-resources/junior-travel-ambassadors\"\u003eJunior Travel Ambassadors \u003c/a\u003e scheme, children play an active role in road safety lessons at hundreds of London schools. For example, by running competitions, making posters and taking turns to be their school's Road Safety Officer.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"strong\"}",
     "We launched our new \u003ca href=\"/corporate/safety-and-security/road-safety/teens-and-young-peoples-road-safety\"\u003eStop Think Live\u003c/a\u003e ad campaign to alert teenagers to the dangers of not paying attention on or near roads. Supported by famous faces like Rizzle Kicks, each poster shows a young person dead after they were distracted by a mobile phone or MP3 player when crossing the road.",
     "For more educational materials, see our page on \u003ca href=\"/info-for/schools-and-young-people/teaching-resources\"\u003eteaching resources for schools and young people\u003c/a\u003e ."
    ],
